Candace K. BeineckeBorn: 26-Nov-1946Gender: FemaleRace or Ethnicity: WhiteOccupation: AttorneyNationality: United StatesExecutive summary: Chairman of Hughes Hubbard & Reed    University: BA, New York University (1967)    Law School: JD, Rutgers University School of Law (1970)    Administrator: Director, Trinity Episcopal School Corporation (1988-95)    Hughes Hubbard & Reed Chairman (1999-)
    Member of the Board of Alstom (2001-)
    Member of the Board of Arnhold & S. Bleichroeder Advisors (as Chairman)
    Member of the Board of Rockefeller Financial Services 
    Member of the Board of Rockefeller & Co. 
    Bill Bradley for President     Fund for New York's Future Board of Directors
    Merce Cunningham Dance Foundation Board of Directors
    Metropolitan Museum of Art Visiting Committee, Thomas J. Watson Library    Friends of Hillary     Hillary Clinton for President     McCain 2000     New York State Bar Association 1971    Partnership for New York City Vice Chair    Women's Forum 





